column5: Took a trip east today.  Anybody fishing?   A couple of photos from the old town.   I thought this was funny.
that last pic is funny, nice.
Good stuff, Rob. I can hear the canon dude yelling to his captain. " Sir, we's gunna need bigger balls!"
Saving that picture   Good picture of Quinte and Picton bay. I wonder if they know it's wrong pointing a firearm.
Thx for sharing. The canon pointing at the ship
Maybe not Roy, there are about 40 cannons all pointing at the harbour. I guess someone figured that is where an attack would come from.  Heading home tonight, I'll post a few photos soon.
Well it doesn't quite work that way if you know the history of Fort Henry.  Have a safe trip back, Rob.
